Subject: Portcullis Security Advisory 05-008


Portcullis Security Advisory
 
Vulnerable System: 
      
Webseries Payment Application
 
Vulnerability Title:  
 
Poor Password Change Implementation
 
Vulnerability discovery and development: 
 
Portcullis Security Testing Services
 
Affected systems: 
 
Bottomline Webseries Payment Application 
 
Details:
 
The change password functionality does not require a user to enter their
current password.
 
Impact:
 
From a system with a valid user logged in it is a trivial matter for a malicious 
user to change the password of a valid user and gain full access to the account.
 
Exploit:
 
No exploit code required
 
